**What You Can Do Next**

**Immediate Actions for Crisis Level:**
• Contact emergency services if in immediate danger
• Reach out to local crisis hotlines for support
• Secure immediate shelter if needed
• Connect with emergency assistance programs

**Safety Note:** If you're in immediate danger, please contact emergency services. This guide provides general information and should not replace professional advice.

**Need More Help?**
This automated guide provides personalized suggestions based on your assessment. For specific questions about programs or services, please contact local service providers or use the resources referenced in your assessment results.
